cs.OM, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the use of spreadsheets for developing decision support systems for solving combinatorial programming problems. This falls under the category of Operations Research (cs.OM) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for solving similar problems. Additionally, the paper discusses the practical application of the approach in the context of procurement and supply chain management (cs.CE).
